To convert a text in UTF8 into speech, follow the following steps in that order

$> perl UTF8toIT3.pl Telugu_PhoneSet_Hts.txt <text.UTF8> <text.IT3> telugu
$> ./parser <text.IT3> Telugu_PhoneSet_Hts.txt
$> ./concatenate wordpronunciation syllables Telugu_PhoneSet_Hts.txt

This will create audio file voice.wav which the speech of the given text 

